  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You expend some of your rage to throw one opponent at another.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Str 13, Con 13, rage class feature, Improved Bull Rush, Power Attack, base attack bonus +6.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>While raging, when you attempt a bull rush combat maneuver, you can spend 1 additional round of your rage as a swift action to add your Constitution bonus on your combat maneuver check to the bull rush. Further, if you bull rush an opponent into a square another creature occupies or into a solid object, the opponent and the creature or object take bludgeoning damage equal to your Strength modifier + your Constitution modifier.",
